    .desc = Merges 2 pipes into one. Items coming from the exit move straight on.
ent-DisposalJunctionFlipped = { ent-DisposalJunction }
    .desc = Merges 2 pipes into one. Items coming from the exit move straight on.
    .suffix = flipped
ent-DisposalYJunction = Т-образная утилизационная труба
    .desc = Merges 2 pipes from the side to one. Items coming from the exit leave through the right entrance instead.
ent-DisposalXJunction = утилизационный соединитель 3-1
    .desc = Merges 3 pipes into 1. Items coming from the exit move straight on.
ent-DisposalBend = изгиб утилизационной трубы
    .desc = A tube bent at a 90 degree angle.
ent-DisposalSignalRouter = сигнальный маршрутизатор мусора
